title: Pence says 'Trump is wrong' to say then-vice president had the right to overturn 2020 election - CNN
content:
1. Pence says 'Trump is wrong' to say then-vice president had the right to overturn 2020 election  CNN
  2. Donald Trump 'Is Wrong' on Authority to Overturn Election, Says Pence  The New York Times

description: Former Vice President Mike Pence called out his former boss by name on Friday, saying that "President (Donald) Trump is wrong" in claiming that Pence had the right to overturn the 2020 election on January 6, 2021.
